tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE therapy_notes (
  note_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  session_date DATE,
  therapist_name VARCHAR(50),
  session_notes TEXT,
  progress_report TEXT,
  treatment_plan TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE session_notes (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  therapist_id UUID,
  session_date DATE,
  session_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE progress_reports (
  report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  therapist_id UUID,
  report_date DATE,
  progress_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE session_notes (
    note_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    therapist_id INT NOT NULL,
    note_text TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE progress_reports (
    report_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT NOT NULL,
    therapist_id INT NOT NULL,
    report_text TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
